No one is coming.

610
00:30:16,440 --> 00:30:17,480
Get over here.
Eat with us.

611
00:30:17,750 --> 00:30:18,750
Quick!

612
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:37,400
Today, eat all you want.

613
00:30:37,640 --> 00:30:39,050
As much as you like, hear me?

614
00:30:39,880 --> 00:30:41,080
