Misters.

616
00:30:47,030 --> 00:30:48,030
Misters!

617
00:30:48,160 --> 00:30:49,190
This melon's really sweet!

618
00:30:49,200 --> 00:30:50,200
Yeah.

619
00:30:50,510 --> 00:30:51,510
Sure is!

620
00:30:51,680 --> 00:30:52,460
This watermelon

621
